assets.description:
Part 1 of 6
A fighter engages with some goblins

Part 2: https://vr.google.com/objects/e9hUieeyEaO?e=VrZandriaUiM1

I made this series of pieces to practice dealing with motion in a scene. Each tries to convey progression of the fight. And each uses the previous as a base, building onto it to continue the story. I like the way that damage persists between parts and the environment evolves.
